data.eml:eml: Type specimens of beetles (Insecta: Coleoptera) at the museo entomológico Francisco Luís Gallego, Medellín, Colombia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sepúlveda-Cano, Paula A., Ramírez-Mora, Manuel A. (2009): Type specimens of beetles (Insecta: Coleoptera) at the museo entomológico Francisco Luís Gallego, Medellín, Colombia. Zootaxa 2017: 65-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.186008
